- `/home/hj/2026/project/adelie-investment/frontend/src/hooks/useAgentControlOrchestrator.js` (lines 271-281)
- `/home/hj/2026/project/adelie-investment/frontend/src/utils/agent/buildActionCatalog.js` (lines 1-26)
